All create and probably update operations should be run under transaction or with commit after them (transaction
is recommended). Read operations can run without it, but there is no reason to doing so - all are safe to be run
under transaction, but some operation only do "db.flush()"

```
    book_title = await BookTitleService.create_book_title(db, data)
    await db.commit()
```

or

Recommended:
```
    async with db.begin():
        book_title = await BookTitleService.create_book_title(db, data)
```